description:
Banner Set: Roselle, Galfin, Dhorme, Farm, Regal and Shiznee.
A hanging banner with the crest of the (Imperial Knight Guardsmen, Mountain Corps, Scolars' Association, Farming Society, royale, Church of Shiznee) sewn on.
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop (General Store in Yano Market) when you purchase it.
name: Banner Set
